如果你真係要試，Ignazio Casis 唔夠。別忘了瑞士是一個真正的民主國家。他們有不同議員來處理不同的事務，你可以嘗試揾以下委員會議員啲個人tweeter account 去煩佢地<br />
(1) 外交事務委員會（FAC）<br />
<a href="https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/committees/specialist-committees/committees-fac" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parlament.ch%2Fen%2Forgane%2Fcommittees%2Fspecialist-committees%2Fcommittees-fac&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=8821e730" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/committees/specialist-committees/committees-fac</a><br />
(2) 安全政策委員會（SPC）或<br />
<a href="https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/committees/specialist-committees/committees-spc" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parlament.ch%2Fen%2Forgane%2Fcommittees%2Fspecialist-committees%2Fcommittees-spc&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=63ef7c3a" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/committees/specialist-committees/committees-spc</a><br />
(3) 經濟事務和稅務委員會（EATC）<br />
<a href="https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/committees/specialist-committees/committees-eatc" data-sr-url="https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parlament.ch%2Fen%2Forgane%2Fcommittees%2Fspecialist-committees%2Fcommittees-eatc&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=2e97c5ab" data-auto-link target="_blank">https://www.parlament.ch/en/organe/committees/specialist-committees/committees-eatc</a><br />
